line_1: And yet I fear I'm i' the wrang,
line_2: O JENNY dear, I've courted lang,

line_1: And yet I fear I'm i' the wrang,
line_2: I've telt my tale and sung my sang,

line_1: An' now ye see ye hae been wrang,
line_2: Nae mair o' me ye'll make a sang,

line_1: That makes us right or wrang.
And rascals whyles that do him wrang,
line_2: Ev'n that, he does na mind it lang:

line_1: Wad gar you trow ye ne'er do wrang,
line_2: The Poets too, a venal gang,
